Greenpeace Afrique, ONG ya kobatela environnement mpe zamba, esengi lisusu mokonzi ya Congo démocratique, Félix Tshisekedi, koboya misala minso ya boluki to ya kozuwa pétrole na parc ya Solnga, na Cuvette Centrale. 
 ONG eye eyebisi ete ezuwaki te eyano ya malonga na mokanda etindaki le 21 juin 2018 na Premier ministre Bruno Tshibala, Union européenne, elongo na Etats-Unis, Canada mpe Suisse.
Greenpeace ekundoli ete Cuvette Centrale etondisami to ezipami na ba tourbières (mabele etonda charbon to mabanga ya makala) eye bato na zebi (chercheurs scientifiques) bamonaki kala te mpe bakanisi ete ebombi milliards 30,6 ya tonnes ya carbone.



